  <h1><span class="muddy">Muddy</span><span class="turnip">Turnip</span></h1>
  <h3>Code analysis</h3>
  <p>MuddyTurnip is a GitHub app that uses white box AI to analyse a repo's code quality. 
  It highlights the problematic files and shows whether the quality drops or improves with a commit.</p>
  <p>Use it to find your worst code to clean up in your public repos before an interview, 
  or alternatively to silently monitor outsourcers.</p>
